<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Google Clone</title>

<style>
body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    text-align: center;
}

/* Top Right Links */
.nav {
    position: absolute;
    top: 10px;
    right: 20px;
}

.nav a {
    margin: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: black;
}

/* Center Content */
.container {
    margin-top: 150px;
}

.logo {
    font-size: 50px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #4285F4;
}

.search-box {
    margin-top: 20px;
}

input {
    width: 400px;
    padding: 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
}

/* Buttons */
.buttons {
    margin-top: 20px;
}

button {
    padding: 10px 15px;
    margin: 5px;
    border: none;
    background: #f2f2f2;
    cursor: pointer;
}

/* Footer */
footer {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 100%;
    background: #f2f2f2;
    padding: 10px;
}
</style>

</head>
<body>

<div class="nav">
    <a href="#">Gmail</a>
    <a href="#">Images</a>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <div class="logo">Google</div>

    <div class="search-box">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Search Google...">
    </div>

    <div class="buttons">
        <button>Google Search</button>
        <button>I'm Feeling Lucky</button>
    </div>
</div>

<footer>
    <p>India</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
Output:
Gmail   Images

              Google

         [ Search Bar ]

   [ Google Search ] [ I'm Feeling Lucky ]


